<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idbc21410e-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s2344"><num value="2344">§ 2344.</num><heading> Cash sales</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">All sales shall be for cash, and the buyer shall arrange for the necessary financing, except as provided in subchapter V of this chapter.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idbc21410f-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/act/1955-08-04/ch543">Aug. 4, 1955, ch. 543</ref>, ch. 5, § 54, <ref href="/us/stat/69/477">69 Stat. 477</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
